  "title": "Executive Administrator",
  "description": "<p><p>Handle daily administrative operations, including correspondence, filing, and document control.</p></p><p><p>Prepare and manage quotations, invoices, payment vouchers, and basic accounts coordination.</p></p><p><p>Maintain project records, contracts, variation orders, and handover documents.</p></p><p><p>Coordinate schedules, site meetings, and follow-ups with clients, suppliers, and subcontractors.</p></p><p><p>Support management in procurement tracking, cost documentation, and approval workflows.</p></p><p><p>Assist in tender submissions, compliance documents, and internal SOP implementation.</p></p><p><p>Ensure proper record-keeping, accuracy, and confidentiality across all company documents.</p></p>",
